text: Pawan Wickramasinghe (born 1 February 1994) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Nondescripts Cricket Club in the 2013–14 Premier Trophy on 31 January 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Nondescripts Cricket Club cricketers Category:Cricketers from Colombo
